  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1556195">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1556195/" class="title-link">翻翻走走</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1556195"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ychdj136/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2734450-30.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ychdj136/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">疯狂の夏虫</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-11-15"
      class="main-meta">2008-11-15 14:47:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1556195_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  参禅之初，看山是山，看水是水；禅有悟时，看山不是山，看水不是水；禅中彻悟，看山仍是山，看水仍是水。   松风流水千年调，抱得琴来不用弹  二者亦是读此书真过程，真感受。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1556195/#comments">(3回应)</a>
